{"id":616303,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/08/【麻辣总局】这是习主席看过的马桶/","date":"2019-08-28T03:37:13Z","modified":"2019-08-28T03:38:12Z","title":"【麻辣总局】这是习主席看过的马桶","content":"<p>近日，网传一张疑似企业的宣传图片，声称某型号的“无水排放马桶”是“习主席看过的马桶”。由于习近平对“厕所革命”的高度关注，近年来我们不乏看到习近平在居民家中视察时，除掀锅盖外，同样也会进行如厕条件的认真检查。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EDAvWh6UwAE0PsV.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-616313\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EDAvWh6UwAE0PsV.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EDAvWh6UwAE0PsV.jpg 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EDAvWh6UwAE0PsV-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/EDAvWh6UwAE0PsV-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>以下疑似该厂商所宣传的马桶型号：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/厕所3.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-616316\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/厕所3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"359\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/厕所3.jpg 1138w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/厕所3-300x196.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/厕所3-768x501.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/厕所3-1024x669.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/厕所3-230x150.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/厕所.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-616314\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/厕所.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"387\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/厕所.jpg 643w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/厕所-300x211.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/厕所2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-616315\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/厕所2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/厕所2.jpg 663w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/厕所2-300x209.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">爱吗，肚子笑痛了。以前掀锅盖看吃的怎么样，现在掀马桶盖看拉得怎么样。这样一条龙掀盖子的“人民领袖”这世上绝对找不到第二个！😂😂😂😂 <a href=\"https://t.co/qXkm1zd7YR\">https://t.co/qXkm1zd7YR</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 阿宝虎丫 (@Jiangliamy1020) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Jiangliamy1020/status/1166157023609856000?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 27, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>习近平近年来对“厕所问题”高度关注</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/5a1e53f8e329a.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-616317\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/5a1e53f8e329a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"253\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/5a1e53f8e329a.png 450w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/5a1e53f8e329a-300x169.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/08/%e3%80%90%e5%bc%82%e9%97%bb%e8%a7%82%e6%ad%a2%e3%80%91%e6%b1%9f%e8%a5%bf%e6%88%90%e7%ab%8b%e5%8e%95%e6%89%80%e9%9d%a9%e5%91%bd%e9%a2%86%e5%af%bc%e5%b0%8f%e7%bb%84/\">【异闻观止】江西成立“厕所革命”领导小组</a></p>\n<p><a title=\"【麻辣总局】连农村厕所这种事儿您都想到了\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/03/%e3%80%90%e9%ba%bb%e8%be%a3%e6%80%bb%e5%b1%80%e3%80%91%e8%bf%9e%e5%86%9c%e6%9d%91%e5%8e%95%e6%89%80%e8%bf%99%e7%a7%8d%e4%ba%8b%e5%84%bf%e6%82%a8%e9%83%bd%e6%83%b3%e5%88%b0%e4%ba%86/\">【麻辣总局】连农村厕所这种事儿您都想到了</a></p>\n<p><a title=\"奇闻录 | 县长当所长\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/12/%e5%a5%87%e9%97%bb%e5%bd%95-%e5%8e%bf%e9%95%bf%e5%bd%93%e6%89%80%e9%95%bf/\">奇闻录 | 县长当所长</a></p>\n<p><a title=\"奇闻录 | 大国领袖目前最关心的事\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/%e5%a5%87%e9%97%bb%e5%bd%95-%e5%a4%a7%e5%9b%bd%e9%a2%86%e8%a2%96%e4%ba%ba%e7%9b%ae%e5%89%8d%e6%9c%80%e5%85%b3%e5%bf%83%e7%9a%84%e4%ba%8b/\">奇闻录 | 大国领袖目前最关心的事</a></p></blockquote>\n<p>近期，在习近平视察古浪县村民家中时，同样出现了与“无水马桶”的合影。</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>习近平：老百姓的幸福就是共产党的事业</p>\n<p>2019-08-22 13:09  来源：中国政府网</p>\n<p>富民新村地处甘肃省古浪县黄花滩生态移民区，习近平总书记21日上午来到这里，看望从山区生态移民易地扶贫搬迁的乡亲们。他走进村民李应川家，小院洁净、住房敞亮、厨卫设施齐全。在客厅坐下来，李老汉拿出一张搬迁前的老照片给总书记看，曾经居住的土坯房同窗明几净的新居有天壤之别。习近平对这里群众生产生活条件发生的巨大变化感到十分欣慰，李老汉连连感叹现在日子太幸福了。习近平强调，你们高兴我们也高兴，共产党就是为人民服务的，就是为老百姓办事的，让老百姓生活更幸福就是共产党的事业。（文字记者：张晓松、朱基钗 摄影记者：鞠鹏、谢环驰）</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/W020190822475827780944.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-616309\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/W020190822475827780944.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"525\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/W020190822475827780944.jpg 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/W020190822475827780944-300x287.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/08/W020190822475827780944-220x210.jpg 220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n","author":970,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,13789],"tags":[13222,33574,38758,38759]}